snippet.title: Hope: The other Side of Adventure - ENGLISH FULL GAME Playthrough - All Endings
snippet.description:
Content Warning: Ab*se, S*icide 

I've played and recorded this using an emulator called LDPlayer. 
Thank you to Izzzyzzz for bringing my attention to this game!
This video contains the bad ending and the good ending.
If there are any other endings I've missed, let me know.

Download for the English Version (found by @otterly_done)
https://apkdownload.com/down_Hope-Other-side-of-adventure/com.MrRoboto.Hope.html

Download for LDPlayer
https://www.ldplayer.net/
